Giving in Action


Support Student Success






Support Student Success






            We are igniting a new standard in education.
          Heading link



 
Copy link



One where old models are upended and new ideas are sparked. Where access and excellence converge, creating opportunity for hungry students from every culture, race, socioeconomic background and circumstance. The future is our fuel, as we leap ahead to craft the university experience the world doesn’t even know it needs yet.






            "Thank you for investing in my future."
          Heading link



 
Copy link


















            With your help in this campaign, we will redefine the model for student experience and success by:
          Heading link



 
Copy link




Ensuring that every hungry mind, in the Chicago region or the world, has a path to study at our great university.
Reaching new heights in preparing thoughtful global citizens for a diverse 21st century driven by a knowledge economy.
Improving student learning by equipping faculty with novel teaching technologies and techniques.
Creating and refining the state-of-the-art spaces needed by today’s students for learning, living, and discovering.







